.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-PAY-FEE-KURTOSIS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-pay-fee-kurtosis \- FEAT-2834 node-pay-fee-kurtosis
